name: Ignition
description:
You feel your body press against the firmament behind you. The undeniable fear of freedom fills your very bones. Not fear that you will actually break free, but fear that freedom is a lie. You will find out either way, oh sojourner. 




Journey on...
A series of collaborations between Wax//Wane and Nate Hill
This is the first in a series of four. If you collect all four you will be airdropped a fifth piece that is the key to something more...
Music by Wax//Wane and images by Nate Hill
